Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:25.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey, is there a shrine nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:29.76,natsume,,0,0,0,,I think there's a shrine once you pass through those bushes there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:29.73,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,神社なら その藪を抜けたところに確か
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:30.83,natsume,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:30.54,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:34.55,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おい 夏目 何だあいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.47,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey, Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:34.81,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's up with him?
