Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:57.86,natsume,,0,0,0,,He's kind of hard to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:57.16,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんか話かけづらいっていうかさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:00.76,natsume,,0,0,0,,"What are you doing," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.96,0:03:00.39,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何やってんだ か
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:02.87,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous that you can't see them.
