Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:49.04,ed-trans,,0,0,0,,If I turned my ear to my thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.97,0:22:57.90,JP_ED-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}聴こえし友の面影
